{"tid":210544,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"開個學英文group 每日share 必學生字(2)","createTime":"2017-04-21T04:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T03:54:35.000Z","uid":74663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"420baaaa0de532f05a893347d2c50c0eb8f2305f","tid":210544,"uid":74663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:38:45.000Z","msg":"上一個post提到 想開個telegram <br />\n定時share 英文生字<br />\n又會抽下書確保你地有記到入腦<br />\n因為私補 經驗話我知 開英文最大問題係無人逼你背生字 學埋幾多skills都無用<br />\n<br />\n估唔到反應非常熱烈 多謝咁多位巴打支持<br />\n因為人數聚多<br />\n決定分一分流<br />\n依家開左3個group<br />\n因為程度唔同 想學既vocab深淺都唔同<br />\n一個係for 想dse 拎level 3/4既人<br />\n一個係for 想dse 拎5or above 既人<br />\n呢兩個gp主要發放d考試主導既字<br />\n一d考評局考過要識既字<br />\n<br />\n一個係for 其他唔係考dse 但係想進修英文既人<br />\n<br />\nlink 係度 自己想join邊個就join 邊個啦<br />\n爆post 之日我就會deactivate 條link 架啦 <br />\nnon dser<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAw7Xt_3dFPRTFeACA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAAw7Xt_3dFPRTFeACA&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=b8bd6655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAw7Xt_3dFPRTFeACA</a><br />\n<br />\naim 4 or below<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAlL24Ex2Ci0OSW67w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAAlL24Ex2Ci0OSW67w&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f6d5caf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAlL24Ex2Ci0OSW67w</a><br />\n<br />\naim 5 or above<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAxFRtnv5jgGufkRuQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAAxFRtnv5jgGufkRuQ&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=fc54019f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAxFRtnv5jgGufkRuQ</a><br />\n<br />\n因為驚之前留左名既人睇唔到 特登開多左個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f56b0c7bacf9e83bd0a7b550afd250f5cdfae3e","tid":210544,"uid":74663,"l